    <p>Varies by country. Generally available from research suppliers, but regulations differ significantly across member states.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mc">
    <h4 style="color:var(--plum);">Russia</h4>
    <p>Most studied here. Epithalamin has been used in clinical settings, and the research infrastructure is strongest in St. Petersburg.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mc">
